  <h2>API Access</h2>

  <p>
    The canonical REST API and MCP surfaces live in Valter's documentation. To
    request access, send an email with your name, organization, intended use case,
    and which ecosystem integration you want to consume.
  </p>

  <p>
    If the question is about jurisprudence and reasoning, Valter is the entry
    point. If it is about legislative or doctrinal grounding, mention whether the
    integration should involve Leci, Douto, or a workflow through Juca.
  </p>

  <h2>Wait List</h2>

  <p>
    Interested in being notified when new features are available? Send an email
    with subject "Wait List" to <a href="mailto:diegomeyersens@gmail.com">diegomeyersens@gmail.com</a>.
  </p>
